Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Young's final diplomacy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040byhq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Aug 1979
Resigning Andrew Young's last act of diplomacy before leaving his UN ambassadorial role. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less